{
  "stem": "26276.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To show everybody that-- to show off that body and to let them know what's going to happen if anybody else is going to try something like this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no reaction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just pass by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Either you look up to the body or you look down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you're in a situation where you don't know how long that's going to go on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody almost gave up that you're never going to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I did give up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did give up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing is, I though I have to wait for my next-- I mean, I just didn't want to run out and try to escape because I knew that if they're going to shoot me, they're going to shoot me at the lake, or on the platz, or that I'm still going to be useful for them.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't shoot especially anybody to kill and a lot of the guards, they would say, the bullet is worth more than a Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Jewish life is not worth the price of a bullet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were trying to save the bullet for something better than that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were trying to kill you in another way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then when we became, after that-- you know, so that you walk to work like an animal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the winter, when we had to walk to work eight kilometers each way, and we had wooden slippers on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, they were slippers with a rag, you know, material on top.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The soles were made out of wood about an inch thick.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
